cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper discusses the characteristics and enabling technologies of non-terrestrial systems in the context of 6G wireless networks, which are primarily related to networking and information theory (cs.NI and cs.IT). The evaluation of the performance of an NTC scenario also involves aspects of augmented reality (cs.AR) and system engineering (cs.SY). Additionally, the use of millimeter wave frequencies for satellite communication is a topic of interest in the field of millimeter wave technology (cs.MM).
